&lt;p&gt;Audiologist&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Audiology Department, Kettering General Hospital&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Band 5 : £24,907- £30,615 per annum&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a motivated and qualified Audiologist to join our busy and friendly team to help us deliver a comprehensive range of Diagnostic Audiology procedures and hearing aid fittings to Adults and children including those with complex needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for someone who has experience with Fittings, DR&#39;s, repairs, ENT clinics (including children Over 5 years old) and reviews.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Although based at Kettering General Hospital we also have clinics at Irthingborough and Corby that would be part of a weekly rota therefore access to your own transport is essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name Shekhar Purohit&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title Chief Audiologist&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number 01536 492136&lt;/p&gt;
